{"tid":1224001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"將矛頭指向醫管局總部，唔係醫院","createTime":"2019-06-15T01:04:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T07:29:18.000Z","uid":241657,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"06e417a6f9f6e640d3f919a8602466e48394613d","tid":1224001,"uid":241657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T01:04:06.000Z","msg":"要醫管局高總部坐向office又唔洗醫人的高層交代番件事：<br />\n1）有無將病人資料交比警方<br />\n2）有的話用什麼準則去比<br />\n3）係邊個將資料比警方<br />\n4）仲有邊個Authorize九龍中GMN要拎取員工放病假資料<br />\n<br />\n我知好多巴打好嬲，但要攪清楚係邊度落order先。醫院班醫生其實好多都唔滿意HA總部班人，覺得佢地唔係做實事。<br />\n如果攪到醫院醫護人員，影響前線的醫療，會令好多人反感。"},{"pid":"5dd7680c31b8a95a7d7675bdb8ff66e04b8cbf0e","tid":1224001,"uid":157938,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T01:16:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>反送中, 撤回修例.<br />\n<br />\n星期日出去遊行.<br />\n<br />\n星期一出去集會</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"63037138b7cceea923157460cb1fdf524b11f383","tid":1224001,"uid":22362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T01:22:59.000Z","msg":"開槍同老屈學生單嘢 黑警講咩都唔洗信<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1223654\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1223654</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"54b04f006199e9d2d65c7815215a68d0b8e68b6e","tid":1224001,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T01:30:42.000Z","msg":"法國黃背心運動的 8 堂課<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1219915\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1219915</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"200c4cc237e6dd9ded30cc1a8e7c7deb38c242d8","tid":1224001,"uid":12633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T01:33:15.000Z","msg":"醫管局坐office果啲正仆街"},{"pid":"a383d67d589896c53770dd59b524a2b5c19f6146","tid":1224001,"uid":53805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T01:35:31.000Z","msg":"但有傳既醫院<br />\nkh qeh hkch<br />\n都係under kcc <br />\n唔排除係kcc cgm 個八婆自把自為邀功<br />\n(打完之後發覺咁似.....)"},{"pid"